Data Source Detail:
From our social growth tools we observe in real-time a user’s content discovery, consumption and social engagement across 4.5MM+ domains. By using the billions of data points that pass through our platform, we filter them into our three core signal categories that indicate interest and intent.

1) Discovery – search, click-back on shared content
2) Consumption –page category and page content
3) Social Engagement – shares on 80+ social channels

Based on these 3 core signals, we create user profiles for any audience, interest and/or behavior in real-time. These profiles are the basis of our Audience Segments and deliver unique signals, scale and quality to Data Buyers.

From our social growth tools we observe in real-time a user’s content discovery, consumption and social engagement across 4.5MM+ domains. By using the billions of data points that pass through our platform, we filter them into our three core signal categories that indicate interest and intent.

1) Discovery – search, click-back on shared content
2) Consumption –page category and page content
3) Social Engagement – shares on 80+ social channels

Based on these 3 core signals, we create user profiles for any audience, interest and/or behavior in real-time. These profiles are the basis of our Audience Segments and deliver unique signals, scale and quality to Data Buyers.

Segment Name: ShareThis > ShareThis_US > Seasonal > Red Carpet
Segment Description: Recent interest from social activity; observed from social sharing, searched page visits and click-backs on shared pages
Data Source Detail:
From our social growth tools we observe in real-time a user’s content discovery, consumption and social engagement across 4.5MM+ domains. By using the billions of data points that pass through our platform, we filter them into our three core signal categories that indicate interest and intent.

1) Discovery – search, click-back on shared content
2) Consumption –page category and page content
3) Social Engagement – shares on 80+ social channels

Based on these 3 core signals, we create user profiles for any audience, interest and/or behavior in real-time. These profiles are the basis of our Audience Segments and deliver unique signals, scale and quality to Data Buyers.

Data Source Detail:
From our social growth tools we observe in real-time a user’s content discovery, consumption and social engagement across 4.5MM+ domains. By using the billions of data points that pass through our platform, we filter them into our three core signal categories that indicate interest and intent.

1) Discovery – search, click-back on shared content
2) Consumption –page category and page content
3) Social Engagement – shares on 80+ social channels

Based on these 3 core signals, we create user profiles for any audience, interest and/or behavior in real-time. These profiles are the basis of our Audience Segments and deliver unique signals, scale and quality to Data Buyers.

Segment Name: ShareThis > ShareThis_DE > Arts & Entertainment > Celebrities & Entertainment News
Segment Description: Recent interest from social activity; observed from social sharing, searched page visits and click-backs on shared pages
Data Source Detail:
From our social growth tools we observe in real-time a user’s content discovery, consumption and social engagement across 4.5MM+ domains. By using the billions of data points that pass through our platform, we filter them into our three core signal categories that indicate interest and intent.

1) Discovery – search, click-back on shared content
2) Consumption –page category and page content
3) Social Engagement – shares on 80+ social channels

Based on these 3 core signals, we create user profiles for any audience, interest and/or behavior in real-time. These profiles are the basis of our Audience Segments and deliver unique signals, scale and quality to Data Buyers.
